Requirements:

Functional Requirements
1. Must use JavaFX for coding
2. Maintain patient information
  a. Add patient to system
  b. Edit Patient information
  c. Update patient treatments
3. Track patient's status of illness
4. Track previous treatments and dosages
5. List specialists clinics
6. List off doctors and specialists
7. Schedule treatment options
8. Track attendance of clinic appointments
9. Create easy-to-use GUI for users
10. Create username and password functionality for users
11. Fetch user information from MySQL Database
12. Allow user input for patients and doctor information
13. Reminders for appointments
14. Secure encryption
15. Protection from SQL Injections
16. Alert safety feature to primary care doctor if patient misses an amount of appointments and/or medication

Non-functional Requirements
1. Must be able to be organized by various categories like name, illness, and clinic
2. Information must be able to be quickly accessed and edited
3. Remove old, outdated, or unnecessary informations
4. Patients and Doctors have a different GUI w/ different options
